  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed hip to gable conversion, by reason of changing the existing roof form would have a detrimental visual impact on the building and its siting within the group of buildings it forms part of, and therefore also the appearance of the St Mark’s Conservation Area. The proposal would therefore be contrary to Policy HC1 ‘Heritage conservation and growth’ of the London Plan (2021), Policy LP3 ‘Designated Heritage Assets’ of the Hackney Local Plan LP33 (2020) and Hackney’s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
